The file header indicates that it is a PNG fileâ€Šâ€”â€Ša â€œlosslessâ€ formatâ€Šâ€”â€Šnot a JPG (the former is more readily used for steganography). He makes a working copy and runs another tool, stepic, to extract any data thatâ€™s hidden using the LSB technique:

